            <abstract id="ref3" label="Abstract">The 
                <title ns2:type="simple" render="italic">0 to 9</title> Archive is a collection of correspondence and manuscripts to the editors of 
                <title ns2:type="simple" render="italic">0 to 9</title>magazine, Vito Hannibal Acconci and Bernadette Mayer. 
                <title ns2:type="simple" render="italic">0 to 9</title>was a small avart garde literary magazine from the late 1960's.</abstract>
        </did>
